data.description: Location, Location, Location, exceptional duplex composed of two completely independent units, located on a generous 7,500 square foot lot and strategically located in front of the Marlins stadium. The property is located in an area in transition, bordering new luxury constructions and modern lifestyles, positioning it as a high potential investment in a growing location. With no association to restrict its versatility, this unique investment proposition allows for the combination of a primary residence with additional residential income. Don't miss this exceptional investment opportunity in a privileged location.
